feat(D1): add KakarotAdapter EVM-to-Cairo bridge contract

Implements the Kakarot zkEVM adapter that translates EVM-style calls
from Solidity interfaces (IStarkPrivacyPool) into native Cairo
PrivacyPool contract calls.

Features:
- evm_deposit, evm_transfer, evm_withdraw routing to PrivacyPool
- View function proxying (get_root, get_leaf_count, is_nullifier_spent, etc.)
- Gas price factor for EVM fee translation (admin-configurable)
- Pause/unpause for emergency stops
- Event emission for all routed operations
- Owner-only admin functions

Files: crates/bridge/src/kakarot_adapter.cairo (new), crates/bridge/src/lib.cairo
